node.text: Who remembers a few years ago at Loretta’s when @dangerboydeegan championship was on the line and out of all the motos that day it only rained / dumped on Haidens Moto! node.text: What’s your kid doing this morning⁉️ I promise you that hill is much steeper then it looks. I know it kicked my ass. Growing up racing as a kid we could never afford the good equipment but the one thing I could do was train hard I ran every morning. Did hill sprints multiple times a week. How bad do you want it!! As I told Haiden enjoy this year on the super mini as it’s only gonna get harder once we get the 250 F 👊🏼 #lovetheProcess #moto #running #training
